{
  "video_id": "g-ONUFFt2qM",
  "title": "Why do I make art? To build time capsules for my heritage | Kayla BriÃ«t",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12991.0,
      "end_time": 14663.0,
      "text": "When I was four years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14687.0,
      "end_time": 17582.0,
      "text": "my dad taught me the Taos Pueblo Hoop Dance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17606.0,
      "end_time": 21737.0,
      "text": "a traditional dance born hundreds of years ago in Southwestern USA."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22508.0,
      "end_time": 25427.0,
      "text": "A series of hoops are created out of willow wood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25452.0,
      "end_time": 29314.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re threaded together to create formations of the natural world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29338.0,
      "end_time": 31357.0,
      "text": "showing the many beauties of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31923.0,
      "end_time": 34905.0,
      "text": "In this dance, you&#39;re circling in a constant spin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34929.0,
      "end_time": 36991.0,
      "text": "mimicking the movement of the Sun"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37150.0,
      "end_time": 38662.0,
      "text": "and the passage of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40232.0,
      "end_time": 43491.0,
      "text": "Watching this dance was magic to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43515.0,
      "end_time": 44873.0,
      "text": "Like with a time capsule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44897.0,
      "end_time": 48177.0,
      "text": "I was taking a look through a cultural window to the past."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48201.0,
      "end_time": 50109.0,
      "text": "I felt a deeper connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50133.0,
      "end_time": 53436.0,
      "text": "to how my ancestors used to look at the world around them."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54460.0,
      "end_time": 57795.0,
      "text": "Since then, I&#39;ve always been obsessed with time capsules."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57819.0,
      "end_time": 59447.0,
      "text": "They take on many forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59471.0,
      "end_time": 62556.0,
      "text": "but the common thread is that they&#39;re uncontrollably fascinating"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62580.0,
      "end_time": 64702.0,
      "text": "to us as human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64726.0,
      "end_time": 66892.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re portals to a memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66916.0,
      "end_time": 70729.0,
      "text": "and they hold the important power of keeping stories alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71503.0,
      "end_time": 73612.0,
      "text": "As a filmmaker and composer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73636.0,
      "end_time": 76214.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s been my journey to find my voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76239.0,
      "end_time": 79608.0,
      "text": "reclaim the stories of my heritage and the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79632.0,
      "end_time": 83694.0,
      "text": "and infuse them into music and film time capsules to share."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84838.0,
      "end_time": 87163.0,
      "text": "To tell you a bit about how I found my voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87188.0,
      "end_time": 89458.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to share a bit about how I grew up."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89880.0,
      "end_time": 93271.0,
      "text": "In Southern California, I grew up in a multigenerational home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93296.0,
      "end_time": 95186.0,
      "text": "meaning I lived under the same roof"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95210.0,
      "end_time": 98491.0,
      "text": "as my parents, aunts, uncles and grandparents."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98936.0,
      "end_time": 103559.0,
      "text": "My mother is Dutch-Indonesian and Chinese with immigrant parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103583.0,
      "end_time": 105569.0,
      "text": "and my father is Ojibwe"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105593.0,
      "end_time": 107197.0,
      "text": "and an enrolled tribal member"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107221.0,
      "end_time": 110611.0,
      "text": "of the Prairie Band&#39;s Potawatomi Tribe in Northeastern Kansas."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111238.0,
      "end_time": 114218.0,
      "text": "So one weekend I&#39;d be learning how to fold dumplings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114242.0,
      "end_time": 116547.0,
      "text": "and the next, I&#39;d be traditional-style dancing"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116571.0,
      "end_time": 117768.0,
      "text": "at a powwow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117792.0,
      "end_time": 121170.0,
      "text": "immersed in the powerful sounds of drums and singers."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122405.0,
      "end_time": 125110.0,
      "text": "Being surrounded by many cultures was the norm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125350.0,
      "end_time": 127902.0,
      "text": "but also a very confusing experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128500.0,
      "end_time": 130689.0,
      "text": "It was really hard for me to find my voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130713.0,
      "end_time": 132954.0,
      "text": "because I never felt I was enough --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132979.0,
      "end_time": 136822.0,
      "text": "never Chinese, Dutch-Indonesian or Native enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137381.0,
      "end_time": 140432.0,
      "text": "Because I never felt I was a part of any community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140456.0,
      "end_time": 143888.0,
      "text": "I sought to learn the stories of my heritage"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143913.0,
      "end_time": 146682.0,
      "text": "and connect them together to rediscover my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147254.0,
      "end_time": 150965.0,
      "text": "The first medium I felt gave me a voice was music."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152430.0,
      "end_time": 155225.0,
      "text": "With layers of sounds and multiple instruments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155249.0,
      "end_time": 158906.0,
      "text": "I could create soundscapes and worlds that were much bigger than my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159556.0,
      "end_time": 162436.0,
      "text": "Through music, I&#39;m inviting you into a sonic portal"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162460.0,
      "end_time": 164462.0,
      "text": "of my memories and emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164486.0,
      "end_time": 166668.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m holding up a mirror to yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167538.0,
      "end_time": 170738.0,
      "text": "One of my favorite instruments to play is the guzheng zither,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170762.0,
      "end_time": 172716.0,
      "text": "a Chinese harp-like instrument."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173190.0,
      "end_time": 175494.0,
      "text": "While the hoop dance is hundreds of years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175518.0,
      "end_time": 179313.0,
      "text": "the guzheng has more than 2,000 years of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179337.0,
      "end_time": 182120.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m playing the styles that greatly influence me today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 183673.0,
      "text": "like electronic music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183697.0,
      "end_time": 187679.0,
      "text": "with an instrument that was used to play traditional folk music long ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188235.0,
      "end_time": 191530.0,
      "text": "And I noticed an interesting connection:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 191770.0,
      "end_time": 193508.0,
      "text": "the zither is tuned to the pentatonic scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193532.0,
      "end_time": 197840.0,
      "text": "a scale that is universally known in so many parts of music"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197108.0,
      "end_time": 198293.0,
      "text": "around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198317.0,
      "end_time": 201130.0,
      "text": "including Native American folk songs."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201781.0,
      "end_time": 203703.0,
      "text": "In both Chinese and Native folk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203727.0,
      "end_time": 207984.0,
      "text": "I sense this inherent sound of longing and holding onto the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208800.0,
      "end_time": 211403.0,
      "text": "an emotion that greatly drives the music I create today."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 212603.0,
      "end_time": 216141.0,
      "text": "At the time, I wondered if I could make this feeling of immersion"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 216165.0,
      "end_time": 217322.0,
      "text": "even more powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217347.0,
      "end_time": 219559.0,
      "text": "by layering visuals and music --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219583.0,
      "end_time": 222329.0,
      "text": "visuals and images on top of the music."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222870.0,
      "end_time": 226448.0,
      "text": "So I turned to internet tutorials to learn editing software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 226472.0,
      "end_time": 228569.0,
      "text": "went to community college to save money"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 228593.0,
      "end_time": 229912.0,
      "text": "and created films."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 231120.0,
      "end_time": 232751.0,
      "text": "After a few years experimenting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232775.0,
      "end_time": 236173.0,
      "text": "I was 17 and had something I wanted to tell and preserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236197.0,
      "end_time": 237825.0,
      "text": "It started with a question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238692.0,
      "end_time": 241762.0,
      "text": "What happens when a story is forgotten?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242985.0,
      "end_time": 245655.0,
      "text": "I lead with this in my latest documentary film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 245679.0,
      "end_time": 247196.0,
      "text": "\"Smoke That Travels,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247220.0,
      "end_time": 252505.0,
      "text": "which immerses people into the world of music, song, color and dance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 252529.0,
      "end_time": 257841.0,
      "text": "as I explore my fear that a part of my identity, my Native heritage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 257865.0,
      "end_time": 259870.0,
      "text": "will be forgotten in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 260728.0,
      "end_time": 265217.0,
      "text": "Many indigenous languages are dying due to historically forced assimilation."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 265619.0,
      "end_time": 269237.0,
      "text": "From the late 1800s to the early 1970s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 269261.0,
      "end_time": 271696.0,
      "text": "Natives were forced into boarding schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271720.0,
      "end_time": 275316.0,
      "text": "where they were violently punished if they practiced traditional ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275340.0,
      "end_time": 277610.0,
      "text": "or spoke their native language,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277860.0,
      "end_time": 279317.0,
      "text": "most of which were orally passed down."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 279892.0,
      "end_time": 285567.0,
      "text": "As of now, there are 567 federally recognized tribes in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285591.0,
      "end_time": 287452.0,
      "text": "when there used to be countless more."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 288179.0,
      "end_time": 289779.0,
      "text": "In my father&#39;s words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289803.0,
      "end_time": 293362.0,
      "text": "\"Being Native is not about wearing long hair in braids."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293386.0,
      "end_time": 295802.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about feathers or beadwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 296244.0,
      "end_time": 300634.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about the way we all center ourselves in the world as human beings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 301776.0,
      "end_time": 304750.0,
      "text": "After traveling with this film for over a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 304990.0,
      "end_time": 306500.0,
      "text": "I met indigenous people from around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306524.0,
      "end_time": 308153.0,
      "text": "from the Ainu of Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 308177.0,
      "end_time": 309627.0,
      "text": "Sami of Scandinavia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309651.0,
      "end_time": 310826.0,
      "text": "the Maori"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310850.0,
      "end_time": 312840.0,
      "text": "and many more."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 312108.0,
      "end_time": 315967.0,
      "text": "And they were all dealing with the exact same struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 315991.0,
      "end_time": 318510.0,
      "text": "to preserve their language and culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319168.0,
      "end_time": 322758.0,
      "text": "At this moment, I not only realize the power storytelling has"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 322782.0,
      "end_time": 325174.0,
      "text": "to connect all of us as human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325198.0,
      "end_time": 328300.0,
      "text": "but the responsibility that comes with this power."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328480.0,
      "end_time": 332778.0,
      "text": "It can become incredibly dangerous when our stories are rewritten or ignored,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 332802.0,
      "end_time": 334788.0,
      "text": "because when we are denied identity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 334812.0,
      "end_time": 336353.0,
      "text": "we become invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 336890.0,
      "end_time": 339430.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all storytellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 339705.0,
      "end_time": 344341.0,
      "text": "Reclaiming our narratives and just listening to each other&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 344365.0,
      "end_time": 347817.0,
      "text": "can create a portal that can transcend time itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 348397.0,
      "end_time": 349580.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 349604.0,
      "end_time": 352952.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}